topic.title: I moved over users.json to another computer but it won't log in
topic.body: Hi I'm new . . . set up on a mac, moved over the users.json to a PC and I can see the id in the json, but it's not seeing it there.  Was able to create a new user id on the Mac but I'd like to access the other one.  Suggestions please?

1569172866_1LQUzLxUdiuVZKwr7wiqii7GzGs8i.body: Thank you @randomshits that's helpful.  I'll recreate the move.  I have a question though: I can see the user name from my other computer in the json, and I can also see the new one that I made.  Now I have two, and I want them both.  It's possible to have two in there, right?
